text: Maged Youssef is an archer from Egypt. He was born on 7 January 1978. Youssef competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics.Maged YOUSSEFMaged Youssef == References == Category:1978 births Category:Egyptian archers Category:Olympians for Egypt Category:Living people
